<P>IN TESTIMONY OF THE ESTEEM WHICH THE AUTHOR FEELS, AND AS A MARK OF FRIEND|SHIP, NATURALLY OCCASIONED BY A FAMILY CONNECTION WITH SO AMIABLE A CHARACTER, THIS ESSAY IS, WITH SINCERE REGARD,</P>
